Class MainActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • AppCompatActivity
      • edu.ithaca.iclibrary.MainActivity

  • public class MainActivity
extends AppCompatActivity
    The opening activity of the app. Captures the user's search queries and sends them to ScrollingActivity. The hierarchical parent of all other Activities.
